{"title_page": "ICIMS", "text_new": "{{lowercase title}}\n\n{{Infobox company\n| name = iCIMS, Inc.\n| logo = ICIMS Logo 4C transparent.png\n| type = [[Private company|Private]]\n| industry = [[Software]]\n| foundation = 2000\n| location = [[Holmdel, New Jersey]]\n| key_people = Colin Day, Founder & Chairman; Steve Lucas, CEO\n| products = iCIMS Connect, iCIMS Recruit, iCIMS Onboard, iCIMS UNIFi, iCIMS TextRecruit, iCIMS Offer, iCIMS Attract, iCIMS Nurture\n| num_employees = 1,000\n| homepage = https://www.icims.com/\n}}\n\n'''iCIMS, Inc.''' is a cloud recruiting platform that enables companies to manage and scale their recruiting programs through an end-to-end talent acquisition platform and an ecosystem of nearly 300 integrated partners. The company is based in [[Holmdel, New Jersey|Holmdel]], [[New Jersey]], with offices in Manhattan, NY, Washington, D.C., San Jose, CA and the UK. It was founded in 2000 by current [[Chairman]], Colin Day.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.njbiz.com/article/20140106/NJBIZ01/301069995/iCIMS-tracks-the-top-talent-with-software |title=iCIMS tracks the top talent with software |website=njbiz.com |publisher=NJBiz |accessdate=2015-11-04 |author=Tom Zanki |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150406070832/http://www.njbiz.com/article/20140106/NJBIZ01/301069995/iCIMS-tracks-the-top-talent-with-software |archivedate=April 6, 2015 }}</ref>  iCIMS is an acronym that stands for Internet Collaborative Information Management Systems.<ref name=\"Back to the Basics Philosophy\">{{cite web |last=Kutik |first=Bill |url=http://www.hreonline.com/HRE/story.jsp?storyId=358921620 |title=What Does iCIMS Actually Mean? |publisher=hreonline.com |accessdate=November 4, 2015|date=March 8, 2010}}</ref><ref name=\"ICIMS Moves To Bell Works In Holmdel, NJ\">{{cite web |last=Surden |first=Esther |url=http://njtechweekly.com/art/3452-icims-moves-into-bell-works-marking-milestone-for-company-and-building/ |title=iCIMS Moves into Bell Works, Marking Milestone for Company and Building | publisher=njtechweekly.com |accessdate=November 30, 2017|date=November 27, 2017}}</ref>\n\niCIMS company subsidiaries include: Jobmagic, Inc.,<ref name=\"iCIMS Acquires Social Recruiting Tech Company\">{{cite web |last=Durdin |first=Mike |url=https://www.recruiter.com/i/icims-acquires-social-recruiting-tech-company/ |title=iCIMS Acquires Social Recruiting Tech Company |publisher=recruiter.com |access-date=March 13, 2019|date=September 11, 2012}}</ref> [[TextRecruit]]<ref name=\"iCIMS Acquires Mobile Recruiting Platform TextRecruit\">{{cite web |last=Durdin |first=Mike |url=https://www.globenewswire.com/news-release/2018/01/08/1285296/0/en/iCIMS-Acquires-Mobile-Recruiting-Platform-TextRecruit.html |title=iCIMS Acquires Mobile Recruiting Platform TextRecruit |publisher=globenewswire.com |access-date=March 13, 2019|date=January 8, 2018}}</ref> and [https://www.jibe.com/ Jibe, Inc.]<ref name=\"iCIMS Acquires Jibe to Provide Employers Best-in-Class Candidate Engagement and Recruitment Marketing Capabilities\">{{cite web |last=Pett |first=Carlee |url=https://www.globenewswire.com/news-release/2019/06/18/1870436/0/en/iCIMS-Acquires-Jibe-to-Provide-Employers-Best-in-Class-Candidate-Engagement-and-Recruitment-Marketing-Capabilities.html |title=iCIMS Acquires Jibe to Provide Employers Best-in-Class Candidate Engagement and Recruitment Marketing Capabilities |publisher=globenewswire.com |date=June 18, 2019}}</ref>\n\nIn 2015, iCims partnered with TextRecruit, a communication tool that facilitates the recruiting cycle utilizing emails, talk, and AI.<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.hrdive.com/news/icims-acquires-textrecruit-pointing-to-mobiles-power-in-recruitment-tech/514453/ |title=iCIMS acquires TextRecruit, pointing to mobile's power in recruitment tech|publisher=HRDive |accessdate=10 April 2020|date= 11 January 2018 |author= O'Donnell, Riia}}</ref>. In 2018, iCIMS acquired TextRecruit.<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.globenewswire.com/news-release/2018/01/08/1285296/0/en/iCIMS-Acquires-Mobile-Recruiting-Platform-TextRecruit.html |title=iCIMS Acquires Mobile Recruiting Platform TextRecruit|publisher=GlobesNewswire |accessdate=10 April 2020|date= 8 January 2018}}</ref>\n\nIn 2019, iCIMS was No. 1 in the market share of recruiting technologies, validating the value of talent management and the tools used to find, employ and retain the best candidates.<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.globenewswire.com/news-release/2020/02/28/1992743/0/en/iCIMS-Enables-Customers-to-Hire-More-than-4-Million-People-Reaching-No-1-in-Market-Share-for-Global-Recruiting-Technology.html |title=iCIMS Enables Customers to Hire More than 4 Million People, Reaching No. 1 in Market Share for Global Recruiting Technology|publisher=GlobesNewswire |accessdate=10 April 2020|date= 28 February 2020}}</ref>\n\n==See also==\n*[[List of talent management system companies]]\n* [[Applicant tracking system]]\n* [[Human resource management system]]\n* [[Onboarding]]\n* [[Recruitment]]\n* [[Social Recruiting]]\n* [[Talent Community]]\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* https://www.icims.com/\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:iCIMS}}\n[[Category:1999 establishments in New Jersey]]\n[[Category:Software companies established in 1999]]\n[[Category:Software companies based in New Jersey]]\n[[Category:E-recruitment]]\n[[Category:Software companies of the United States]]\n", "text_old": "{{lowercase title}}\n\n{{Infobox company\n| name = iCIMS, Inc.\n| logo = ICIMS Logo 4C transparent.png\n| type = [[Private company|Private]]\n| industry = [[Software]]\n| foundation = 2000\n| location = [[Holmdel, New Jersey]]\n| key_people = Colin Day, Founder & Chairman; Steve Lucas, CEO\n| products = iCIMS Connect, iCIMS Recruit, iCIMS Onboard, iCIMS UNIFi, iCIMS TextRecruit, iCIMS Offer, iCIMS Attract, iCIMS Nurture\n| num_employees = 1,000\n| homepage = https://www.icims.com/\n}}\n\n'''iCIMS, Inc.''' is a cloud platform recruiting that enables companies to ma